  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1051">
<l>irakka virattakkārk kāṇiṟ karappi </l>
<l>ṉavarpaḻi tampaḻi yaṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you meet with those that may be begged of, you may beg; (but) if they withhold (their gift) it is their blame and not yours.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
